@psoe_minority
title: <span style="color: var(--psoe); font-style: italic;">PSOE</span> Minority Government
subtitle: PSOE governs alone, tolerated from the outside. [? if congreso_coalition_psoe_min_talks: It hangs on concessions we'd have to wring out. ?]
view-if: congreso_coalition_psoe_min_s > congreso_s_majority - 50
choose-if: congreso_coalition_psoe_min_reach and not congreso_coalition_psoe_cs_wtf
unavailable-subtitle: [? if congreso_coalition_psoe_min_s < congreso_s_majority: Even with outside support that could be negotiated, PSOE falls short of investiture. ?][? if congreso_coalition_psoe_cs_wtf: This does not seem to be the plan of [+ psoe_leader +] and [+ csspa_leader +]. ?]
